{"tid":1506292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《記者會》咁其實 市民打警察 都係自然反應來姐","createTime":"2019-08-25T18:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T18:27:00.000Z","uid":66390,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"07598dd9e175fbe3ea324c8a12c205141a6f3a01","tid":1506292,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:13:50.000Z","msg":"0152 #灣仔 #警察總部 <br />\n#警方記者會 <br />\n<br />\n記者：<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">為何警員要踢跪在地上的街坊？為何要舉槍指向記者？</span><br />\n<br />\n答：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當時警員留意到有人做地下有動作，警務人員動作係自然反應。（記者起哄）</span><br />\n<br />\n再次強調，當時警員生命受嚴重威脅，行動屬自然反應。首要目的保護自己個人安全和市民安全。指向記者只因當時很難分辨示威者，暴徒，甚至記者。當時目的是為驅散前面示威者。（記者再度起哄）<br />\n#立場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/71i4T7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F71i4T7g.jpg&h=4c83228a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0zjH0C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0zjH0C.jpg&h=6dc966ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自然反應來姐</span></span><br />\n你怪邊個呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cbf15a15e9b7dc08921876383105a33cd888bc","tid":1506292,"uid":276319,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:14:45.000Z","msg":"以後手足打狗都可以話自然反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cde1a7e8826001fd0da23efbca98c432dc58d29","tid":1506292,"uid":66390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:14: